Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Something is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.80,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}A story is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.43,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you like it?  Do you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.10,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Got any doubts? I don't think so. Let's jump into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.60,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.44,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:27.15,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.74,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let'sgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.78,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bounce, 高鳴る鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.49,OP - JP,,1000,0,0,,{\blur4}No doubts, 感じる波動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.62,OP - JP,,1000,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}研ぎ澄ます感性をCONTROL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.71,OP - JP,,800,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Like a 歌舞伎的 Playing a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.92,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}When you're in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.96,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's a Hero? Break the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.50,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's a Hero? Make new waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.17,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's a hero! Save all the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.38,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You can be who you are & be free yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.55,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}Is this where it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.85,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}No no 終わらない Broken road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:57.47,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4}続くStory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:00.31,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}信じるのは　自分のHEART
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.10,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大義より仁義　異論はなし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.27,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BELIEVE IN YOURSELF
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.15,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}背負った誓い　歪ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.53,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}巻き起こせ　革命REVOLUTION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:11.61,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}挑め世界　沈ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.32,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}舞い上がる　異端NO IMITATION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.95,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}YOU AND I FEEL ALIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.33,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}Overdrive It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:23.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誰がヒーロー？ Break the old ways
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.67,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}お前がヒーロー！ MAKE NEW WAVES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.29,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:31.05,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.88,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.93,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,200)}C-C-Come and kick up! NOW LET'S GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是什么悄然而至
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.80,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}传奇即将拉开序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.43,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你会喜不自胜还是鄙夷不屑？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.10,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亦或者犹豫不决？ 而我心意已决  共赴这传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.60,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.44,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:27.15,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.74,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.78,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}心潮澎湃  热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.49,OP - CN,,0,1000,0,,{\blur4}毋庸置疑  感受波动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.62,OP - CN,,0,1000,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}控制好敏锐的感性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.71,OP - CN,,0,800,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}像歌舞伎那般演绎自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.92,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}当你深陷泥潭  是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.96,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.50,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.17,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是英雄！ 救民济世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.38,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你大可率性而为  逍遥自在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.55,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}可这就是英雄的终点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.85,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}不  艰难险阻永无止尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:57.47,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4}传奇还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:00.31,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}坚守本心  矢志不移
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.10,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}仁义高于大义  无可辩驳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.27,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.15,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}一言九鼎  驷马难追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.53,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}揭竿而起  掀起革命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:11.61,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}挑战世界  宁死不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.32,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}展翅高飞  去做那绝无仅有的异端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.95,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}感受彼此生命的共振
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.33,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}放手一搏  全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:23.16,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.67,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是英雄！ 独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.29,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:31.05,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.88,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.93,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,200)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:22.70,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}孤独な　影が伸びて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:28.91,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕日が今日も　乾いた大地に消える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:34.79,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さすらう　渡り鳥は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:42.30,ED - JP,,150,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}すり切れた　羽を引き継ぎ　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.85,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}滑稽に　みえ見えるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.44,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}泥にまみれても　這い上がるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.86,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Becuase we're loose stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.90,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}最後の時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.28,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Catch the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.28,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}止めない　翼広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:10.91,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}戦う者たちに　レクイエムはいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.04,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Sky high
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:17.50,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}想いは遥か高く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:25.47,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雲を切り裂いて　あの空の彼方へと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.82,0:22:22.70,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}孤独的身影被余晖拉长
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.70,0:22:28.91,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}今日 夕阳照旧沉落在干涸的大地尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.91,0:22:34.79,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那只漂泊的候鸟
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.79,0:22:42.30,ED - CN,,150,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}拖着伤痕累累的羽翼 缓步前进
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.85,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}他人眼里 这很可笑吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.44,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即便满身泥泞 也要奋勇斗争
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.86,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}只因为我们是桀骜的星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.90,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}直至最后一刻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.28,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}乘风破浪
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.28,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}势不可挡 展翅高飞
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.28,0:23:10.91,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}英勇的战士无需安魂曲
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.04,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}天高任鸟飞
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.29,0:23:17.50,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}思念飞向遥远的彼方
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.50,0:23:25.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}冲云破雾 直至世界尽头
